<i>noun</i>: 사움 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사움</dt><br>
<dd>the third pillar of Islam is fasting (primarily during the month of Ramadan); Muslims abstain from food and drink and gambling and all sensuous pleasures from sunrise to sunset during Ramadan</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: sawm</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
